      "content": "fair enough. but when you look at the actual numbers for the last 10 years, isn't it pretty obvious that the increased benefits have basically acted as a disincentive for people to get back into the workforce? it feels like the data points pretty clearly to a downward pressure on participation caused by the welfare expansion.",
